Package uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.data.element.id

Interface EdgeId

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementId, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Edge, EdgeSeed, LazyEdge
    public interface EdgeId
extends ElementId
    An EdgeId is an interface describing the core methods that are required in order to identify an Edge.
